  andress co - starred with elvis presley in the 1963 musical film , fun in acapulco , with frank sinatra and dean martin in 4 for texas ( 1963 ) , opposite marcello mastroianni in the 10th victim ( 1965 ) , alongside john richardson in she ( 1965 ) , as the countess in the blue max ( 1966 ) , and with another bond girl claudine auger in anyone can play ( 1967 ) .

movie geography : elvis presley had " fun in " this mexican resort city with ursula andress -- who would n't ?

acapulco